mongod, then open new tab and node keystone!



Create new section:

1. add view template: clone templates/views/index.js > new_page.jade (holds markup in Jade)
2. add view route: clone routes/views/index.js > new_page.js (adds route for this view)
3. add route to index.js: app.all('/new_page', routes.views.new_page)
4. add links to nav (found in middleware)
